// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1602 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d2ec4c9d-d965-568b-bf72-2f557758320f

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
